channel.title: I cant delete this file!help!
channel.description:
Ok, I want to get rid of my old server folder, because I dont need it. But It cant delete somethings because of some character files. Here is what it says, "Cannot delete (name): Cannot find the specified file. Make sure you specify the correct path and file name." When I click the file, it asks me what to open it with, but I choose all of them, none of them work. I cant move it either. HOW DO I FIX THIS PLEASE!!
Edit- When I try to delete the file as a whole, it says "Cannot delete file: Cannot read from the source file or disk".
